    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as reliable, functional transportation for its next owner. The exterior shows some clear coat peeling on the hood and roof, along with various small dings and scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear and some minor staining. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it may require some routine maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
